Body: Description: We are in plan to migrate existing production EPP appliance from old ubuntu 18.x to 22.x. we have configured the external client to server communication channel via netscaler. Needing to confirm the configuration need at the netscaler for this migration effort. Is there option to enhance some of the security at netscaler and/or client & server. Wanting to schedule a call with technical resources.
Invitation updated. Attendees: Emil Podar, William Lau
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed

Next Steps Updated: The database was migrated to the new EPP Server.
Everything seems fine and the customer requested to keep the ticket open for a few more days, to make sure that everything works as expected
What We've Learned Updated: Customer wanted to migrate the EPP Server to a newer VM
